\id TIT - Biblica® Open Kiyombe Contemporary New Testament and Psalms 2002
\h TITE
\toc1 Nkanda Polo kuidi Tite
\toc2 Tite
\toc3 Tite
\mt2 Nkanda Polo kuidi
\mt1 Tite
\c 1
\s1 Thonono
\p 
\v 1 Polo, kisadi ki Nzambi ayi mvuala wu Yesu Klisto, boso buididiminu ki batu bobo basobolo ba Nzambi ayi boso buididi nzayilu yi mambu ma kiedika madi boso buididi khinzukulu yi mambu ma Nzambi,
\v 2 mu diana di luzingu lukalumani. Luzingu lolo Nzambi yoyi yika yilendivuna ko kavanina tsila tuamina thonono yi zitsungi.
\v 3 Vayi thangu bu yifuana, niandi wuzabikisa mambu mandi mundongolo yoyi ndiyekodolo boso buididi lutumunu lu Nzambi Mvulusi eto,
\v 4 mfidisidi nkanda wawu kuidi Tite khatika, muanꞌama mu minu kioki tuidi mu kithuadi.
\p Bika nlemvo ayi ndembama bi Nzambi Tata ayi bi Klisto Yesu Mvulusi eto bibanga yaku.
\s1 Mbiekolo yi mintuadisi mu dibundu
\p 
\v 5 Bila ndibikila ku Kelete kiawu kiaki : wukubika mambu moso masiala ayimuingi wubieka mintuadisi mi Dibundu mu kadika divula boso bu nditumina.
\v 6 Kadika ntuadisi kabika ba bila kioki kafueti sembolo ; kafueti ba bakala dikuela nketo wumosi kaka ; beki bana bakuikama. Batu babika baka diluaku di fundila bana benit i khadulu yimbimbi badi voti batumiminanga batu ko.
\p 
\v 7 Didi diambu di mfunu ti ntuadisi wu dibundu kafueti ba mutu kambulu tsembolo banga kisadi ki Nzambi wunkambu tulanga diana mu diela diandi, kafuemanga nsualu ko ; kanuanga malavu ko ; kanuananga ko, kabika ba mutu weti zola baka zimbongo mu mayuya.
\v 8 Kafueti ba mutu zebi yakulanga bumboti banzenza ayi kafueti ba mutu weti zola mamboti ; kafueti ba mutu wu diela, mutu wusonga, mutu wuvedila, zebi kukiyala.
\v 9 Kafueti ba wukangama mu mambu ma kuikama boso buididi malongimuingi kaba wufuana mu lubula boso buididi malongi ma kiedika ayi mu bedisila bobo bamfindisanga ziphaka.
\s1 Lubuka mu diambu di minlongi mi luvunu
\p 
\v 10 Bila bawombo kaba tumamananga ko, banyolukanga mambu ma phamba ; bamvunanga batu. Badi bawombo muidi Bayuda.
\v 11 Bufueni mu kuba kangisa miunu bila zinzo ziwombo balembo zimbisabu beti longa mambu ma kambulu fuana mu diambu di babaka zimbongo mu luvunu.
\p 
\v 12 Wumosi mu bawu, mbikudi awu veka wutuba ti :
\q1 \qt Basi Kelete badi bankua luvunu\qt*
\q1 \qt badi bibulu bimbimbi,\qt*
\q1 \qt ayi kisalu kiawu dia kaka ayi badi miolo.\qt*
\p 
\v 13 Kimbangi kiaki kidi ki kiedika. Diawu wuba temina ngolo muingi baba minu ki kiedika
\v 14 ayi babika singimina mu zinongo zi Bayuda ayi zithumunu zi batu bobo beti vengama mu mambu ma kiedika.
\p 
\v 15 “Bibioso bidi bivedila mu diambu di batu bobo badi bavedila” vayi bibioso bisi bivedila ko mu diambu di batu bobo badi basumuka ayi bakambulu minu ayi diela diawu ayi mayindu ma mintima miawu bidi bisumuka.
\v 16 Muaki bambanzilanga ti bazebi Nzambi vayi bantunukanga Nzambimu mavanga mawu bila baba zolanga ko ; basi bulemvo ko ayi balendi vangakadi diambu dimosi di mboti ko.
\c 2
\s1 Zithumunu mu diambu di makabu ma phila mu phila ma minkuikizi
\p 
\v 1 Vayi ngeyo, tuba mambu mafueni mu malongi ma kiedika.
\v 2 Longa babakala bayunduka babika ba phulu yi dia ayi yi nua, baba batu ba lukinzu, batu ba nzayilu ; baba batu ba badi minu ki kiedika, batu ba luzolo lu kiedika ayi baba batu badi mvibudulu.
\p 
\v 3 Bobuawu, baketo bayunduka baba baketo banzingilanga mu khadulu yifueni kuidi baketo banlongo ; babika ba kifu kitembikisanga mambu mabatu, babika kukiyekulanga mu nuanga malavu mawombo. Baba baketo banlonganga mambu mamboti
\v 4 muingi balonga baketo bobo bakuedidi bosi mu zola babakala bawu ayi bana bawu,
\v 5 baba diela, baba bavedila, babelanga zinzo ziawu mayindu ; baba baketo bamboti, batumukinanga babakala bawu mu diambu di mambu ma Nzambimabika vuezo.
\p 
\v 6 Bobuawu, lubula bamatoko muingi mabika ba phulu yi dia ayi yi nua.
\v 7 Mu mambu moso ngeyo veka ba kifuani mu mavanga mamboti. Bika malongi maku maba mavedila ayi ma lukinzu.
\v 8 Mambu maku maba masonga, makambu bila kioki mafueti tubudulu muingi batu bobo bankakidila bafua tsoni bu bakambulu diambu di mbimbi dituba mu diambu dieto.
\p 
\v 9 Lubula bavika baba bulemvo kuidi bapfumu ziawu, mimonisanga bapfumu ziawu khini mu mambu moso. Bosi mibika findisanga bapfumu ziawu ziphaka.
\v 10 Mibika yibanga, vayi mimonisa kikhuikizi ki kiedika muingi malongi ma Nzambi, Mvulusi eto makinzuku mu mambu moso.
\s1 Nlemvo yawu tho yi phulusu
\p 
\v 11 Bila nlemvo wu Nzambi wunnatanga phulusu wumonika kuidi batu boso.
\v 12 Wukutulonganga muingi tubika lenzanga Nzambi, tubika zinzinunuzi ntoto. Vayi tuzingila mu tsungi yayi, mu kambu phulu yi dia ayi yi nua. Tuzingila mu busonga, mu khinzukulu yi Nzambi
\v 13 bu tulembo vingila diana di khini ayi mbonokono yi nkembo yi Nzambi eto yinneni ayi Mvulusi eto Yesu Klisto.
\v 14 Wukiyekula niandi veka mu diambu dieto muingi katukula mu mambu moso mambimbi ayi muingi kavedisa, mu diambu diandi veka, batu bobo kavuidi niandi veka ayi bobo bantulanga bufula mu vanganga mavanga mamboti.
\p 
\v 15 Longa mambu momo, lubula ayi temina mu lulendo loso lu tumina. Mutu kabika ku lenza.
\c 3
\s1 Khadulu yi Baklisto
\p 
\v 1 Bika wutebula batu boso moyo ti bafueti ba bulemvo kuidi minyadi ayi bapfumu. Bosi bafueti ba tumamana ayi bafueti ba bakubama mu vanganga mavanga mamboti.
\v 2 Babika finganga kadi mutu wumosi, baba batu ba ndembama ayi batu ba luzitu ayi baba batu bammonisanga nlembami kuidi batu boso.
\p 
\v 3 Bila beto mamveto tutuama ba bivungisi ayi tusia ba bulemvo ko, tuba bazimbala, tuba bavika ba zinzinunu zi phila mu phila ayi zikhini zi phila mu phila ; tuba zingilanga mu luvunu ayi mu kikhenene, batulendaayi mamveto tulendasana beto na beto.
\v 4 Vayi mamboti ma Nzambi, Mvulusi eto, ayi luzolo luandi mu diambu di batu bu bimonika,
\v 5 buna niandi wutuvukisa. Bika sia ti mu diambu di mavanga ma busonga momo tuvanga vayi mu diambu di kiadi kiandi ; bu katusukudila mu nlangu, mu mbutukulu yimona, mu kutukitula bamona mu lusadusu lu Pheve Yinlongo.
\v 6 Niandi wutudukudila Pheve Yinlongo beni mu buwoka mu lusadusu lu Yesu Klisto Mvulusiꞌeto,
\v 7 mu diambu di bu tukitulu basonga mu nlemvo andi muingi tukitukabatu bela vinginina kiuka boso buididi diana di luzingu lu kalumani.
\v 8 Mambu momo madi makuikama ayi thidi ti wumalongila mu bufula muingi bobo bawilukila Nzambi bakiyekula mu ba batheti mu vanganga mamboti. Mambu mama madi mamboti ayi ma mfunu kuidi batu.
\s1 Buevi buzingila ayi batu bobo bannatanga khabunu
\p 
\v 9 Vayi tinanga biuvu bi buvungisi, mambu ma kikhulu, minzonza ayi ziphakamu diambu di Mina bila masi mfunu ko ayi mambu moso momo madi ma phamba.
\v 10 Vayi kuidi mutu wulembo totula khabunu, ngeyo kunlubula mu khumbuyitheti ayi yimmuadi. Buna kadi buela ba yandi kithuadi.
\v 11 Bila zaba ti mutu wuphila yoyi wuzimbala ayi wumvolanga masumu ; ayi wukukibedisanga niandi veka.
\s1 Zindubu zi tsuka
\p 
\v 12 Mu thangu ndiela kufidisila Alitemasi voti Tishike buna vika mu kuiza kuidi minu ku Nikopolisi bila ndibeki lukanu lu viokisila kuaku tsungi yi kiozi kingolo.
\v 13 Tomba busila mu sadisa bumboti zuzi Zenasi mu nzietolo andi ayi Apolo muingi babika kambu kadi kima.
\v 14 Bufueni batu beto veka balonguka mu ba batheti mu vangangamavanga mamboti mu diambu di mambu ma mfunu muingi bedi kambu mimbutu.
\s1 Zimboti
\p 
\v 15 Baboso badi yama kuaku bafidisidi mboti. Vana mboti kuidi batu bobo beti kutuzola mu minu. Bika nlemvo wubanga yeno beno boso.
